---------------------
Title      : Cargo.toml has no categories field
Description: crates.io uses the `categories` field to classify packages.
             Without it Renderflow will not appear in the `command-line-utilities`
             or `development-tools` categories, reducing discoverability.
Affected   : Cargo.toml
Impact     : Low — reduces crates.io discoverability.
Status     : FIXED in this session
Fix Applied:
  categories = ["command-line-utilities", "development-tools", "text-processing"]

